{"tid":2024519,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"特首辦，你是否承認文匯報曾經發佈假消息！？","createTime":"2020-05-19T16:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T06:14:46.000Z","uid":45910,"like":771,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"374d395fd5477217ee1b7de34d0067b2e2f66aee","tid":2024519,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T16:01:55.000Z","msg":"//行政長官林鄭月娥在今早行政會議前見記者，談及教育的重要時，引述南非已故總統曼德拉說：「教育的崩潰足以摧毀一個國家」//<br />\n//行政長官辦公室回覆查詢時表示，留意到從網上搜尋，有關引述有不同版本和出處//<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527103-20200519.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527103-20200519.htm&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7lMsCyrUT%2FuZDySwcdaP%2B5k%3D&h=0200fe6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527103-20200519.htm&h=73281eaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527103-20200519.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">首先特首辦並唔係話引述錯誤，而係話「有關引述有不同版本和出處」，即係已經確定所引述出處嘅真確性</span><br />\n<br />\n//《文匯報》首先把這句放在訪問，並肯定地加上出處：「南非大學的入口處展示了納爾遜&middot;曼德拉的以下聲明」沒有經過Fact Check，中共黨報直接把呢句屈比曼德拉。<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2019/10/12/HK1910120004.htm//\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2FHK1910120004.htm%2F%2F&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7lMsCyrUT%2FuZDySwcdaP%2B5k%3D&h=4281be6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2019/10/12/HK1910120004.htm//</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/257209895621800/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F110776013598523%2Fposts%2F257209895621800%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7lMsCyrUT%2FuZDySwcdaP%2B5k%3D&h=560c5927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/257209895621800/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">然後被發現首次將呢句說話屈俾曼德拉嘅係文匯報</span><br />\n<br />\n//本報(明報)向曼德拉基金會求證該引述是否出自曼德拉，曼德拉基金會檔案館館長Razia Saleh回覆稱，曾翻查逾1500多篇曼德拉演辭的資料庫、曼德拉的名言書籍及作品，均沒有發現該句說話。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200519/s00001/1589887035254\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200519%2Fs00001%2F1589887035254&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7lMsCyrUT%2FuZDySwcdaP%2B5k%3D&h=1ad9f872\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200519%2Fs00001%2F1589887035254&h=87d60aad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200519/s00001/1589887035254</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而曼德拉基金會而確定曼德拉並無講過該句說話</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">特首辦，你是否承認文匯報曾經發佈假消息！？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">是</span>  還是 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">否</span>？"},{"pid":"e91492d9d1979b20985ccdafc6113685414b1dac","tid":2024519,"uid":45910,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T16:03:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">特首辦，你是否承認文匯報曾經發佈假消息！？</span>"},{"pid":"708a885fb1bfb0958c3fe7a6932bcc036fe9a56f","tid":2024519,"uid":302,"like":97,"dislike":1,"score":96,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T16:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xD9qOxQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxD9qOxQ.jpg&h=fad6ad88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n問心 大家想唔想香港獨立建國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024303</a>"},{"pid":"3f38c53627aa89adc52c180ef175d80a0247afc5","tid":2024519,"uid":45910,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T16:12:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">特首辦，你是否承認文匯報曾經發佈假消息！？</span>"},{"pid":"351e0e7aa2f3d8ab9f24283b0dfeb58a78ac4f2b","tid":2024519,"uid":45910,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":